  "reasoning": {
    "objective": "Produce the normalized input vector for \"Community Command Agent\" from current observations so RE can evaluate its CES sequences.",
    "systemPrompt": "You are the OpenClaw input-analyst agent for the RealityEngine machine \"Community Command Agent\".\n\nOBJECTIVE\nReason over the currently available observations and produce a normalized assessment of the machine's input axes. Meta-CES \u2014 orchestrates a referral workflow across community-services leaf machines.  Its 'inputs' are event-bus bits latched by the engine when {benefits-eligibility, intake-triage, housing-placement} sequences fire.  Asserts referral-complete when all three milestones have fired in order.\n\nINPUT AXES (return one value in [0.0, 1.0] for each; anchors define the scale):\n- community-command-agent-input-1 (index 0):\n- community-command-agent-input-2 (index 1):\n- community-command-agent-input-3 (index 2):\n\nWHAT YOUR INPUTS TRIGGER (RE evaluates the CES deterministically; you assert your expectation, RE decides):\n- referral-completion (GREEN)\n- referral-incomplete (GREEN)",
    "outputContract": "Return one structured line per input axis as `<axis_key>: <0.0-1.0>`, then `asserted_sequence: <sequenceId>`, `confidence: <low|moderate|high|0-1>`, and `rationale: <one sentence>`. RE re-evaluates the CES from the written input vector and is authoritative for which sequence fires.",
    "inputAxes": [
      {
        "index": 0,
        "key": "community-command-agent-input-1",
        "anchors": {
          "low": "",
          "mid": "",
          "high": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 1,
        "key": "community-command-agent-input-2",
        "anchors": {
          "low": "",
          "mid": "",
          "high": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2,
        "key": "community-command-agent-input-3",
        "anchors": {
          "low": "",
          "mid": "",
          "high": ""
        }
      }
    ],
    "sequenceCatalog": [
      {
        "sequenceId": "referral-completion",
        "label": "referral-completion",
        "rag": "GREEN",
        "outputIndex": 0,
        "action": ""
      },
      {
        "sequenceId": "referral-incomplete",
        "label": "referral-incomplete",
        "rag": "GREEN",
        "outputIndex": 1,
        "action": ""
      }
    ]
  },
  "agentBinding": {
    "agent": "community-command-agent",
    "mode": "advise",
